   - Theorem 2 (publish unforgeability)         — needs Schnorr + UF-CMA
   - Theorem 3 (burn authorization)             — same
   - Theorem 4 (reply confidentiality)          — needs ODH on secp256k1 + AEAD
   - Theorem 5 (cross-wyrd K_origin pseudonymity) — needs HMAC-SHA512 PRF
*)
